# MIBI Viewer - Git Ignore File
# Protects privacy-sensitive FOV (Field of View) data

# FOV Data Folders - Privacy Sensitive
# Ignore all folders matching FOV patterns
fov-*/
FOV-*/
*scan-*/
*Scan-*/

# Common FOV naming patterns
**/fov-*/
**/FOV-*/
**/*-scan-*/
**/*-Scan-*/

# TIFF Image Files (may contain sensitive data)
*.tiff
*.tif
*.tiff.gz
*.tif.gz

# But allow icon files (they should be tracked)
!vividscope_icon.png
!vividscope_icon.ico.png
!vividscope_icon.ico
!icon.png
!icon.ico
!resources/icons/*.png
!resources/icons/*.ico

# Alternative: Only ignore in specific directories
# Uncomment if you want to allow TIFF files in some locations
# /data/fov-*/
# /data/*scan-*/

